headline: Thursday Earnings Preview: Look to These Banking Giants for Key Consumer Insights
summary: Wednesday's earnings reports from some major banks are just the appetizer. On Thursday, the main course will be served up by Morgan Stanley, Goldman Sachs, PNC, and U.S. Bancorp.
